flowchart TD
  intent_source[意图与需求源]
  intake[求职意图 Intake]
  source_planning[岗位来源规划]
  job_cards[岗位卡片与索引]
  scoring[解释性评分排序]
  proposal_gate[Proposal 与审批门禁]
  execution_guard[安全执行边界]
  artifacts[状态与审计 Artifacts]
  records_sync[项目记录与同步]
  operation_surface[操作入口与前端展示]
  intent_source -->|scope| intake
  intake -->|route selection| source_planning
  source_planning -->|approved readonly sources| job_cards
  job_cards -->|normalize + compare| scoring
  scoring -->|next action proposal| proposal_gate
  proposal_gate -->|sensitive action check| execution_guard
  execution_guard -->|write audit trail| artifacts
  execution_guard -->|document result| records_sync
  artifacts -->|renderable state| operation_surface
  records_sync -->|docs + board| operation_surface
